<teaserText grammarName="coremedia-richtext-1.0"><div xmlns="http://www.coremedia.com/2003/richtext-1.0" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><p>At Perfect-Chef.com we are always looking for YOUR best recipes. Enter your favourite recipe now and win shopping coupons every month!</p></div></teaserText>
<detailText grammarName="coremedia-richtext-1.0"><div xmlns="http://www.coremedia.com/2003/richtext-1.0" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><p class="p--heading-2">Win coupons<br/></p><p>Here is your chance to win Perfect-Chef.com shopping coupons every month.</p><p>Share your favorite recipes along with a photo of your culinary creation - to prove to our community that you are a Perfect Chef!</p><p><br/></p><p class="p--heading-2">Voting</p><p>Our Jury votes for the best recipes and we highlight each month's winner in the Recipe section of our site.</p><p>Of course you can also comment on and rate the recipes you love.</p><p>Please note that recipes will only be published on our site once they have been reviewed by our moderators.</p></div></detailText>
